delete, remove, overwrite, or replace Meta control-plane state unless the
affected state is archived first and the archive is compressed under a reviewed
workspace evidence path such as `var/lib/codex-runtime-gate/archives`,
`artifacts`, `snapshots`, or `var/log/raw`.

The original Meta project set includes `loop_lib`, `meta_plugin_protocol`,
`meta_core`, `meta_git_lib`, `loop_cli`, `meta_cli`, `meta_git_cli`,
`meta_project_cli`, `meta_rust_cli`, and `meta_mcp`. Add-on repos such as
